Text: I tried the password generator but still comes up as invalid....What am I doing wrong

@ Bobbamax,

I'm sorry to hear that - worked fine for me.  Try typing in your name, make sure that iScrapbook 4 is selected from the drop-down and click generate. Then double click the number and paste it into the licensing section of the app.

DP
Sorry for the late reply, but thanks for the heads up polisdavid, i got it to work thanks to you
